com.microsoft.azure.documentdb

Class StoredProcedureResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.StoredProcedureResponse

  • public final class StoredProcedureResponse
extends Object
    Represents the response returned from a stored procedure. Wraps the response body and headers.
